Add Image Viewer translations to all 38 languages

This commit adds complete translations for the new Image Viewer feature
to all 38 supported languages (excluding en-US which already has them).

Changes:
- Added settings_destination_viewer to all language files
- Added 12 viewer_* strings to all language files
- Total: 494 new translations (13 strings × 38 languages)

Languages updated:
- Western European (10): de-DE, de-x-franconia, es-ES, fr-FR, fr-QC, 
  it-IT, nl-NL, pt-PT, pt-BR, ca-CA
- Nordic (4): da-DK, fi-FI, nn-NO, sv-SE
- Eastern European (12): cs-CZ, et-EE, hu-HU, lt-LT, lv-LV, pl-PL, 
  ro-RO, ru-RU, sk-SK, sl-SI, sr-RS, uk-UA
- Middle East (5): ar-SY, el-GR, fa-IR, he-IL, tr-TR
- Asian (6): id-ID, ja-JP, ko-KR, vi-VN, zh-CN, zh-TW
- Other (1): kab-DZ

Translation quality:
✓ Used Translation Glossary for consistency
✓ Maintained language-specific conventions
✓ Preserved technical elements (ellipsis, loanwords)
✓ Applied dialect variations (Franconian, Quebec French)
✓ Proper RTL support (Arabic, Hebrew, Persian)
✓ All 38 files validated for XML well-formedness
✓ Code review passed with no issues

